  "Description": "The RDA5807MP is a fully integrated CMOS FM tuner that receives FM stereo broadcasts from 50 MHz to 115 MHz. It incorporates a digital low‑IF receiver with synthesizer, IF selectivity, RDS/RBDS decoder, MPX decoder, and stereo audio DACs, requiring minimal external components. It is controlled via an I²C interface and includes an integrated LDO regulator, making it suitable for portable devices.",
